[BID 4H]
@S @v(bid|bids) 4\H. Holding three-card heart support for partner's promised five-card suit, @s @v(raise|raises) to game in the 5-3 heart fit, becoming declarer so the lead comes up to the strong hand.
[show NS]
Well judged. North's 3\S over 2\D pinpointed five hearts and four spades, and South's three small hearts gave the eight-card fit. Playing 4\H from South protects the \HKQ from the opening lead — exactly what Smolen is designed to achieve.}
